com.sap.integration.anywhere.dto

Class AnwInventoryCountingPostLineDto

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.integration.anywhere.dto.AnwInventoryCountingPostLineDto

  • public class AnwInventoryCountingPostLineDto
extends java.lang.Object
    Object used for Inventory counting. It represents line of Inventory Counting payload in which are stored information about product and its quantity. Inventory Counting line is slightly different for HTTP GET and HTTP POST, that is the reason why exists two objects AnwInventoryCountingGetLineDto and AnwInventoryCountingPostLineDto.
